des: Having a hard time deciding what G Fuel Flavor you wanna make? Well, give the G Fuel Randomizer a spin! This Randomizer includes all current tubs as of March 2020 (Note: this Randomizer does not include limited or discontinued flavors such as Lemonade, Coconut, Exc.)
